		PRINTFORM  [{COUNT, 2, RIGHT}] - %NAME:COUNT, 26, LEFT%(歌唱技能:{ABL:COUNT:歌唱技能, 2, LEFT} 演奏技能:{ABL:COUNT:演奏技能, 2, LEFT} 舞踊技能:{ABL:COUNT:舞踊技能, 2, LEFT}
